      "content": "That feeling of completion can be overwhelming, even if your physical journey is still ongoing. It often happens when the external excitement fades and the internal need for novelty clashes with the reality of the current moment. Sometimes, the only way to move past this is to intentionally create new reasons to keep going, whether it's a new destination or simply a different way of experiencing the one you're in.",
      "source": "target",
